74
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:47,360
Allez trouver Huo Kaiming.

75
00:05:47,370 --> 00:05:49,100
Mon grand, reste ici et attends un appel.

76
00:05:49,100 --> 00:05:50,210
Vous autres, partez !

77
00:05:51,170 --> 00:05:52,050
M. Chen.

78
00:05:52,050 --> 00:05:52,890
Songge.

79
00:05:54,170 --> 00:05:55,050
Qu'est-ce qui ne va pas?

80
00:05:55,050 --> 00:05:56,980
Chen Hui et moi étions au studio photo.

81
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:57,840
Huo Kaiming est arrivé,

82
00:05:57,850 --> 00:05:59,370
